snippet.textDisplay:
Conor is looking 👍
If he took boxing training seriously for one year there are a lot of fringe level contenders that he would beat.
I honestly believe that if his cardio conditioning was up to par, he has the skill set to "hold his own" against some of the top fighters in the sport.
Probably won't win, but he goes 10 rounds and looks aok.
Like him or not Conor brings a certain level of excitement to the sport.
If he's on point and back, there's a lot of interesting fights in both MMA and boxing.
I'll definitely be watching and supporting like many more of his🇵🇷fans.
